  "local_port": 47956,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do I make clothes in Roblox?",
  "response": "Creating clothes in Roblox involves a few steps. You can design shirts, pants, and t-shirts using image editing software and then upload them to the Roblox platform. Here's a step-by-step guide to help you through the process:\n\n### Step 1: Get the Right Templates\n1. **Download Templates**: Go to the Roblox website and search for clothing templates. You can find templates for shirts, pants, and t-shirts. These are typically PNG files that you can use as a base for your designs.\n   - **Shirts**: [Shirt Template](https://www.roblox.com/create) (you may need to navigate to the Create section)\n   - **Pants**: [Pants Template](https://www.roblox.com/create)\n   - **T-Shirts**: You can upload any image for a T-shirt but won't need a specific template.\n\n### Step 2: Design Your Clothes\n1. **Use Image Editing Software**: Use programs like Photoshop, GIMP, or any other image editing software to create your design on the downloaded template.\n   - **Editing**: Make sure to stay within the boundaries of the template and consider how the designs will wrap around the character model.\n   - **Save Your File**: Save your design as a PNG file for best results.\n\n### Step 3: Upload Your Design\n1. **Log in to Roblox**: Go to the Roblox website and log into your account.\n2. **Navigate to Create**: Click on the \u2018Create\u2019 tab at the top of the page.\n3. **Upload Your Clothing**:\n   - For **Shirts/Pants**:\n     - Click on \"Shirts\" or \"Pants\" under the \"My Creations\" section based on what you\u2019ve designed.\n     - Click the \"Choose File\" button to upload your PNG design.\n     - Name your item and then click the \"Upload\" button.\n   - For **T-Shirts**:\n     - Click on \"T-Shirts.\"\n     - Click the \u201cChoose File\u201d button, select your design, and then upload it.\n\n### Step 4: Configure Your Item\n1. After uploading, you may want to configure your item by setting up its price, description, etc.\n2. If you plan to sell your clothing, set the price in Robux.\n\n### Step 5: Wear or Sell Your Clothes\n1. **Wear Your Clothing**: Go to your avatar, select the clothing tab, and find your newly uploaded items.\n2. **Selling**: If you have set a price, other players can purchase your clothing.\n\n### Additional Tips\n- **Follow Roblox\u2019s Community Standards**: Ensure your designs comply with Roblox\u2019s guidelines on content.\n- **Promote Your Clothes**: Share your creations with friends and on social media to attract buyers if you plan to sell them.\n\nWith these steps, you can start making and sharing your custom clothing in Roblox!",
